Mark Twain Ebony Tankard Fishtail




Peterson: Mark Twain Ebony Tankard Fishtail




Product Number: 002-029-32485


This hearty Poker shape was released as part of a two-pipe set with the Mark Twain bent Billiard. Here on its own, this firm sitter brings to mind the corn cob pipes of Huck Finn, though its classy jet-black finish and nickel accent band make it perfectly suitable as a dress pipe.

- Rachel DuBose
        




















