Peterson Mark Twain Tankard - Smooth (9mm)
























 




Additional Images:




















Peterson Mark Twain Tankard - Smooth (9mm)



Subscribe below to get notified when this product is back in stock




The Peterson Mark Twain Tankard is one of the two pipes featured in the Mark Twain Collection set. A beautiful, hefty poker, this pipe has a beautiful, polished brown stain and is equipped with a sterling silver band and an ebonite stem that has a fishtail mouthpiece and a 9mm filter.
This pipe comes with its original packaging.















Product 4/4













